channel.title: People help me put my sever online
channel.description:
Hello everyone, my name is Rebirthscape. For about 3 days me and my friends are trying to get our RSPS online, for three straight days. We've been staying up until 5 AM, espically me and trying to fix it! But, everytime we do and my friends try it, "Error connection to server" For me, it works. Does anyone have any suggestions? If you help me, I will make you a part of our staff. Thank you,
Best regards, Rebirthscape.

item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

[quote=“RebirthScape, post:1, topic:402046”]Hello everyone, my name is Rebirthscape. For about 3 days me and my friends are trying to get our RSPS online, for three straight days. We’ve been staying up until 5 AM, espically me and trying to fix it! But, everytime we do and my friends try it, “Error connection to server” For me, it works. Does anyone have any suggestions? If you help me, I will make you a part of our staff. Thank you,

Best regards, Rebirthscape.[/quote]

Possible causes:

  1. They haven’t put in your up in the client.
  2. They don’t the right cache
  3. You haven’t forwarded your ports correctly
  4. Your server isn’t on.
